{"tid":1534342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再諗佢條聲係咪劇本已經無意思, 最緊要諗我地要做乜。","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:08:37.000Z","uid":276951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2c793ef2cf4d4837b8f00e5567eef3004b9aad11","tid":1534342,"uid":276951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"今朝睇完林鄭點答, 就更肯定幾樣野。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">錄音的重點係講咗中共預咗慢慢玩，十一唔係死線，由得香港經濟衰落去，一直用癲狗咬，直到有一日，大家精盡人亡。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾句confirm 幾樣野：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 搞衰香港經濟嚇唔到中共，佢預咗，仲預咗到平靜返會喺大灣區俾著數香港。 (根據本人收到啲風，似係俾著數地產商喺大灣區起樓)<br />\n<br />\n2. 國慶只係場俾大陸人自己睇的大show，中國全民打飛機就夠。 所以喺香港搞國旗，搞國徽，根本都唔係中共在乎嘅野。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n3. 中共無其他招數，就係一直出動狂犬亂咬，直至我地投降。<br />\n<br />\n4. 中共怕兩樣野: (1) 中美貿易戰,&nbsp; Donald Trump 出狠招。 (2) 無得唔認一國兩制玩完。 (2) 好多人覺得而家已經係, 但其實個定義係, 去到幾厚顏都無得唔認的地步, 其實林鄭條錄音流出話自己無得辭職, 已經係呢個級別, 但係林鄭厚顏如此, 一日仲未有人放棄防守, 自爆「習近平唔俾我做乜乜乜」, 一日都仲可以厚顏。你睇之前Reuters 話中共高層唔俾林鄭解決問題, 中央直情出嚟話假新聞, 你睇佢死守咩位, 就知佢最驚乜。就係無得唔認一國兩制玩完。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我地而家要做乜？<br />\n<br />\n上面講咗中共怕美國, 同無得唔認一國兩制玩完。後者其實無辦法, 面對以謊言搵食100年的中共, 除非你諜戰偷情報, 否則無計可施。所以要聚焦中美Trade war。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一，中美貿易戰已經confirm 係唯一我地有機會攻擊的中共要害。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n美國愈多參與，愈多動作，愈會令中共內部陣腳大亂，懷疑自己。 佢地懷疑自己，先有機會乘中共高層內鬥之機，重新覆盤香港政策。 到時五大訴求就成功在望。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地而家要全力同國際，美國社會連結！俾美國人知，你地係救世主！你地係超級英雄！你地就係Captain America! 用對抗極權的同情又好，用英雄主義 the chosen one 又好。 總之要喚起佢地使命感！只要美國義無反顧出手, 香港人就勝利在望! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二，繼續創意+勇武抗爭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭一可以持續爭奪全球注意力；二，可以內部凝聚手足熱情。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n每場運動都係全香港人繼續燃燒的燃料。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家中共準備無限期消耗, 我地都要有呢個準備。KEEP 住團火，香港人就會一齊贏！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多野未玩哂，仲有好多人喺場邊未落場，要用啲創意方法引埋佢地落場，好似人鏈咁，低消耗，又聚到氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三，要增加黑警的發癲成本。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n呢個真係要靠極力保護法庭，司法體制，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要令第一個黑警上法庭</span></span>，咁先係唯一阻嚇到黑警的做法。 至於點做，我唔係好知，可能需要有第一個義士挺身而出指證，寧願同黑警攬炒。 做法，風險，值博率好難講，但唔係無得諗。 有義士可能贏面好高，而自己法律風險好低。 呢個要專業人士諗諗計。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"c87fff5fed5415fa61db144d75fc8976509cb0a9","tid":1534342,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c12f3a4aa6401ae1b4ff4632236969ae71153f45","tid":1534342,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"07c2455d11a2c486ba58941737f36e9e05455f7f","tid":1534342,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaBbTAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaBbTAC.png&h=2beb762c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦一眾考官7號要幫機場重考</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0592c55008d355304de9a621b87e18a90de82940","tid":1534342,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75d2b9d8da14738f418bdf6506550d0d23f42429","tid":1534342,"uid":276957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n好想推但P牌無得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d422c48ea0eb6b19f29a3f582aadd554c5dd7d","tid":1534342,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b2a14dac0ab60641b9158966027f99be46917e23","tid":1534342,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"i agree with u.<br />\n要準備長期作戰，特別係創意抗爭😇<br />\n其實和理非真係真係要全面升級， 捐錢星火612/罷買紅色商戶機就基本消費。 要對抗白色恐怖就要用盡公民的權利：盡情投訴不公義的事， 盡幫抗爭者例如接放學。 大家一齊做係絕對幫到香港人抵抗暴政🤩"},{"pid":"02fd5fa674f082058d44734310744236d88c920f","tid":1534342,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"同意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece7bd58cd7c882f4e6ca27152f7c6e775dd1f26","tid":1534342,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad439c8e8002d5a531475fc4255be46b65876d3f","tid":1534342,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b2a59ac4e4a3d99209dde8f0c889b60c49e73b6f","tid":1534342,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"053f83e474b18105d2dd595e9097a1ce715dfbce","tid":1534342,"uid":276951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"加！油！"},{"pid":"7ca44c0239558f853e88fadf10173e05a7993914","tid":1534342,"uid":185519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"同意，要集中返係我地可以做到d咩。 一定要清算。"}]}